# bat config (read via XDG_CONFIG_HOME=~/.config)
# Make `cat` (aliased to bat) behave like cat: print and return, never page.
--paging=never
# nice default style: line numbers + grid + header (the "prints nice" look)
--style=numbers,changes,header
# theme — ansi adapts to the terminal's Catppuccin colors
--theme=ansi
